36namespace webrtc {
37
38struct Probe {
39 Probe(int64_t send_time_ms, int64_t recv_time_ms, size_t payload_size)
40 : send_time_ms(send_time_ms),
41 recv_time_ms(recv_time_ms),
42 payload_size(payload_size) {}
43 int64_t send_time_ms;
44 int64_t recv_time_ms;
45 size_t payload_size;
46};
47
48struct Cluster {
49 Cluster()
50 : send_mean_ms(0.0f),
51 recv_mean_ms(0.0f),
52 mean_size(0),
53 count(0),
54 num_above_min_delta(0) {}
55
56 int GetSendBitrateBps() const {
57 RTC_CHECK_GT(send_mean_ms, 0.0f);
58 return mean_size * 8 * 1000 / send_mean_ms;
59 }
60
61 int GetRecvBitrateBps() const {
62 RTC_CHECK_GT(recv_mean_ms, 0.0f);
63 return mean_size * 8 * 1000 / recv_mean_ms;
64 }
65
66 float send_mean_ms;
67 float recv_mean_ms;
68 // TODO(holmer): Add some variance metric as well?
69 size_t mean_size;
70 int count;
71 int num_above_min_delta;
72};
73
74class RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime : public RemoteBitrateEstimator {
75 public:
76 RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime(RemoteBitrateObserver* observer,
77 Clock* clock);
78
79 RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime() = delete;
80 RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime(const RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime&) =
81 delete;
82 RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime& operator=(
83 const RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime&) = delete;
84
85 ~RemoteBitrateEstimatorAbsSendTime() override;
86
87 void IncomingPacket(int64_t arrival_time_ms,
88 size_t payload_size,
89 const RTPHeader& header) override;
90 // This class relies on Process() being called periodically (at least once
91 // every other second) for streams to be timed out properly. Therefore it
92 // shouldn't be detached from the ProcessThread except if it's about to be
93 // deleted.
94 void Process() override;
95 int64_t TimeUntilNextProcess() override;
96 void OnRttUpdate(int64_t avg_rtt_ms, int64_t max_rtt_ms) override;
97 void RemoveStream(uint32_t ssrc) override;
98 bool LatestEstimate(std::vector<uint32_t>* ssrcs,
99 uint32_t* bitrate_bps) const override;
100 void SetMinBitrate(int min_bitrate_bps) override;
101
102 private:
103 typedef std::map<uint32_t, int64_t> Ssrcs;
104 enum class ProbeResult { kBitrateUpdated, kNoUpdate };
105
106 static bool IsWithinClusterBounds(int send_delta_ms,
107 const Cluster& cluster_aggregate);
108
109 static void AddCluster(std::list<Cluster>* clusters, Cluster* cluster);
110
111 void IncomingPacketInfo(int64_t arrival_time_ms,
112 uint32_t send_time_24bits,
113 size_t payload_size,
114 uint32_t ssrc);
115
116 void ComputeClusters(std::list<Cluster>* clusters) const;
117
118 std::list<Cluster>::const_iterator FindBestProbe(
119 const std::list<Cluster>& clusters) const;
120
121 // Returns true if a probe which changed the estimate was detected.
122 ProbeResult ProcessClusters(int64_t now_ms)
123 RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(&mutex_);
124
125 bool IsBitrateImproving(int probe_bitrate_bps) const
126 RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(&mutex_);
127
128 void TimeoutStreams(int64_t now_ms) RTC_EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(&mutex_);
129
130 rtc::RaceChecker network_race_;
131 Clock* const clock_;
132 const FieldTrialBasedConfig field_trials_;
133 RemoteBitrateObserver* const observer_;
134 std::unique_ptr<InterArrival> inter_arrival_;
135 std::unique_ptr<OveruseEstimator> estimator_;
136 OveruseDetector detector_;
137 RateStatistics incoming_bitrate_;
138 bool incoming_bitrate_initialized_;
139 std::vector<int> recent_propagation_delta_ms_;
140 std::vector<int64_t> recent_update_time_ms_;
141 std::list<Probe> probes_;
142 size_t total_probes_received_;
143 int64_t first_packet_time_ms_;
144 int64_t last_update_ms_;
145 bool uma_recorded_;
146
147 mutable Mutex mutex_;
148 Ssrcs ssrcs_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&mutex_);
149 AimdRateControl remote_rate_ RTC_GUARDED_BY(&mutex_);
150};
